abstract_ts:
In this paper, we research some properties of Codazzi pairs on almost para Norden manifolds. Let $(M_{2n},\ \varphi ,\ g,G)$ be an almost para Norden manifold. Firstly, $g$-conjugate connection, $G$-conjugate connection and $\varphi $-conjugate connection of a linear connection $\mathrm{
abla }$ on $M_{2n}$ denoted by ${\mathrm{
abla }}^{*\&#x0D; },\ {\mathrm{
abla }}^{\dagger \ }$ and ${\mathrm{
abla }}^{\varphi \ }$ are defined and it is demonstrated that on the spaces of linear connections, $\left(id,\ *,\dagger ,\varphi ight)$ acts as the four-element Klein group. We also searched some properties of these three types conjugate&#x0D; connections. Then, Codazzi pairs $\left(\mathrm{
abla },\varphi ight)\ ,\left(\mathrm{
abla },gight)$ and $\left(\mathrm{
abla },Gight)$ are introduced and some properties of them are given. Let $R\ ,\ R^{*\ }$and $R^{\dagger \ }$are $(0,4)$-curvature tensors of conjugate connections&#x0D; $\mathrm{
abla }\mathrm{\ ,\ }{\mathrm{
abla }}^{*\ }$and ${\mathrm{
abla }}^{\dagger \ }$, respectively. The relationship among the curvature tensors is investigated. The condition of $N_{\varphi }=0$ is obtained, where $N_{\varphi }$ is Nijenhuis tensor field on $M_{2n}$ and it is known&#x0D; that the condition of integrability of almost para complex structure $\varphi $ is $N_{\varphi }=0$. In addition, Tachibana operator is applied to the pure metric $g$ and a necessary and sufficient condition $\left(M,\varphi ,\ g,Gight)$ being a para Kahler Norden manifold is found. Finally, we examine $\varphi $-invariant linear connections and statistical manifolds.
